{
  "texts": [
    "In recent years with the advancement and the enormous success of LLMs, people have almost made them synonymous to AI.Most LLMs are trained via a huge amount of text data and code, that usually comes from data crawlers who are scanning the internet for specific information, but may also contain other sources such as books, articles, and code repositories.",
    "Through several techniques of machine learning (classification, back propagation, reinforcement learning, and others) the researching team trains the model to recognize word patterns and relationships, by adjusting the models' parameters or \"weights\" [22].",
    "The process of adjusting the models' internal parameters to improve predictions is called model optimization.",
    "The final goal is not only to minimize errors in the \"next word prediction\", but also to predict patterns within words and data.",
    "There are several significant advancements in AI technology in the past few months which we will enumerate and analyze their benefits and impact.One of the most impressive technological news to come out recently, involved the company Groq™ which is developing an Application-Specific Integrated Circuit (ASIC) that can \"run\" an LLM much more efficiently and with less power than traditional Graphics Processing Units (GPUs) [23]."
  ]
}